subject: Re:  UNITED BANK OF AFRICA PLC.
body:
Dear Mr. Ricardo,

Thank you for your email. I understand the urgency of the situation and will proceed with the transfer as soon as possible.

However, could you please provide me with more details on how to carry out this transfer? I would appreciate it if you could guide me through the process to ensure that everything goes smoothly.

Looking forward to your prompt response.

Best wishes,
Darrell
